{{version028}}
{{flavour|Drains life from an enemy, healing nearby allies in the process.}}

'''Malign Offering''' is a monster-only spell which offers up the life force of a single target to heal nearby allies of the caster. This spell ignores the target's [[AC]], but can be reduced with [[negative energy resistance]] and requires a clear line of fire.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.19]], [[black sun]]s had this spell.
*This spell was added in [[0.13]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
